OL,6,FFollowing the sentencing, Detective
OL,7,FConstable Anna Haynes, who led the
OL,8,Finvestigation, said: "Such was the
OL,9,Fregularity of his offending, Williams
OL,10,Fwas unable to say how many times he
OL,11,Fhad fraudulently sold his employer's
OL,12,Fstock ` only that he spent most of the
OL,13,Fproceeds on online gambling websites.
OL,15,F"He then tried to cover his tracks by
OL,16,Fproviding inaccurate stock takes and
OL,17,Fdeliberately mismanaging the company's
OL,18,Frecords.
