OL,6,F"Ultimately these concerted efforts
OL,7,Ffailed and he found himself before the
OL,8,Fcourts.
OL,10,F"Since Williams did not have the
OL,11,Fstrength to seek help for his
OL,12,Fspiralling addiction before it was too
OL,13,Flate, a successful business had to
OL,14,Fclose and five staff lost their jobs.
OL,16,F"He did express remorse throughout the
OL,17,Finvestigation and I hope this case
OL,18,Fserves as a reminder to people of how
OL,19,Fgambling can get out of control and
OL,20,Fruin lives."
