OL,3,CManager who stole #240k worth of stock
OL,4,Cadmitted it to employer in text message
OL,6,FWhat happened?
OL,8,FNottingham Crown Court heard he had
OL,9,Fbeen selling the company's solar PV
OL,10,Fproducts to customers at reduced
OL,11,Fprices to make sales, before creating
OL,12,Ffalse invoices that directed payments
OL,13,Finto his own bank account.
OL,15,FAfter delivering the items to
OL,16,Fcustomers himself, he returned to work
OL,17,Fand booked the stock back in ` stating
OL,18,Fon the company's systems that the
OL,19,Fcustomer had cancelled the order.
