OL,6,FTo hide the missing stock in the
OL,7,Fwarehouse, Williams kept the empty
OL,8,Fboxes after delivering the items to
OL,9,Fcustomers and then placed these empty
OL,10,Fboxes back on the warehouse shelves so
OL,11,Fthe stock would not be visibly missed.
OL,13,FText message confession
OL,15,FSuspicions were raised when the firm's
OL,16,Fmanaging director noticed the amount
OL,17,Fof stock in the Nottingham warehouse
OL,18,Fwas not matching up with what Williams
OL,19,Fwas claiming was in there.
