OL,3,CManager who stole #240k worth of stock
OL,4,Cadmitted it to employer in text message
OL,6,FFollowing weeks of conversations and
OL,7,Fexchanged emails, Williams eventually
OL,8,Fsent a text message to the managing
OL,9,Fdirector to confess he had been
OL,10,Fstealing from the business as he had
OL,11,Fan online gambling addiction.
OL,13,FThe next day, 12 July 2018, Williams
OL,14,Fattended Radford Road Police Station
OL,15,Fto confess to his crimes.
OL,17,FWilliams told officers he believed he
OL,18,Fhad taken approximately #70,000 worth
OL,19,Fof stock. However an investigation
OL,20,Ffound the true figure was around
OL,21,F#240,000.
