OL,6,FAs a result of him selling that stock
OL,7,Fat reduced prices, the court heard
OL,8,FWilliams made approximately #150,000
OL,9,Ffrom the two-year fraud.
OL,11,FWilliams was employed as the general
OL,12,Fmanager of PGK Distribution's UK
OL,13,Fbusiness and reported to the firm's
OL,14,Fmanaging director, based at the
OL,15,Fcompany's head office in Australia.
OL,17,FIn a business impact statement, the
OL,18,Fmanaging director said Williams'
OL,19,Factions resulted in the closure of the
OL,20,FUK business, resulting in five job
OL,21,Flosses.
