OL,6,F'Exceptional and merciful course'
OL,8,FJudge Mark Watson said it was a
OL,9,F"sophisticated" scam, but that a
OL,10,Fnumber of factors meant he was
OL,11,Fprepared to take an "exceptional and
OL,12,Fmerciful course" and suspend the
OL,13,Fsentence.
OL,15,FThese factors included his guilty
OL,16,Fplea, lengthy delays in bringing the
OL,17,Fcase to court, his previous good
OL,18,Fcharacter and the effort he has made
OL,19,Fto address his gambling addiction
OL,20,Fsince his arrest.
